o be considered in any future extension of the provisions of this local law or a successor law\\ulnone .\\ul  \\cf0\\ulnone\\par\n\\'a7 3. This local law takes effect immediately.\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar\\qj\\fs18\\par\n\\par\n\\par\n\\ul Session 13\\par\n\\ulnone APM\\par\nLS #10619\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar 9/2/25 6:32pm\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar\\qj\\ul\\par\nSession 12\\par\n\\ulnone EH\\par\nLS #10619\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar 1/17/23\\par\n\\fs24\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar\\fi720\\par\n}\n",
